data.description: Welcome home to Liberty Hall Plantation. This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath is in a neighborhood that has a community pool and play park.   As you enter you will se beautiful wood floors, which flow nicely with this open concept from the living area into the kitchen with a glass black splash and recess lighting. Just off the kitchen is an individual laundry room with additional storage. Upstairs are the bedrooms with a loft / flex area that can be used as an office, play area or tv space.  The master bedroom contains a garden tub/shower and large walk-in closet. Brand new HV/AC unit and water heater. Huge screened porch perfect for entertaining and a large back yard with privacy fence. Assumable VA mortgage available  for those that qualify.
